\paragraph{两个正反核子的散射: $N\bar{N}-N\bar{N}$}
~

下面我们考虑核子-反核子的散射~$N\bar{N}-N\bar{N}$; 我们直接从图写出散射振幅的解析式:
\begin{align}
i\mathcal{M}^{(2)}=&\begin{aligned}\includegraphics[width=1.8 cm]{pic/nn-1.jpg}\end{aligned}+\begin{aligned}\includegraphics[width=2.6 cm]{pic/nn-2.jpg}\end{aligned}\nonumber\\
=&i(-ig)^2\left[\frac{1}{(p_1-p'_1)^2-m^2}+\frac{1}{(p_1+p_2)^2-m^2+i\epsilon}\right].
